<div class="display-inline-block"><button type="button" class="cursor-pointer text-no-underline bg-transparent border-0 padding-0 text-left margin-0 text-normal text-primary" aria-controls="journal_context_menu">Arch Bone Jt Surg</button></div>. 2018 Sep;6(5):353–358.</div>
