</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Short-Term Results of the DePuy Global Unite Platform Shoulder System: A Two-Year Outcome Study</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Updegrove%20GF"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Gary F Updegrove</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Gary F Updegrove</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
